00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:01,600
You're treating us,

864
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:02,840
so who's paying the bill?

865
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:05,270
It's still the company's money.

866
00:39:05,270 --> 00:39:06,240
It's everyone's money.

867
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:07,720
You're pretty sharp about money.

868
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:09,800
Why are you two
playing good cop, bad cop?

869
00:39:10,440 --> 00:39:11,320
My sister

870
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:12,840
hasn't slept well for a week.

871
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:14,000
What did she say?

872
00:39:14,690 --> 00:39:15,600
Bin is right.

873
00:39:15,970 --> 00:39:17,050
This victory

874
00:39:17,060 --> 00:39:18,540
is thanks to Ms. Wen's great efforts.

875
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:19,500
Ms. Wen.

876
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:23,060
- It's all family business.
- Cheers to you.

877
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:24,400
You're too kind.

878
00:39:24,410 --> 00:39:25,520
That's right.

879
00:39:25,730 --> 00:39:28,480
Behind the scenes is more important
than the spotlight, right?

880
00:39:28,720 --> 00:39:30,280
Fan, cheers to you.

881
00:39:30,600 --> 00:39:31,440
You've worked hard.

882
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:33,760
Now I see it clearly.

883
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:35,640
If selling his sister
would get him a wife,

884
00:39:35,640 --> 00:39:37,320
I would've been sold 800 times by now.

885
00:39:38,120 --> 00:39:38,960
Come on.

886
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:41,000
Shouldn't you toast me first?

887
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:42,640
Why?

888
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:45,350
I spent a night at the seafood market.

889
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:47,520
Now my clothes smell like shrimp.

890
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,320
I should toast you.

891
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,160
Right?

892
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:51,510
Wait a minute.

893
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:53,040
I can't.

894
00:39:53,050 --> 00:39:53,940
Do it now.

895
00:39:54,050 --> 00:39:54,920
Wait a minute.

896
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:57,060
You've worked hard too.

897
00:39:58,850 --> 00:40:00,160
Not hard at all.

898
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:03,440
This wine tastes sweet.

899
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:05,460
I've never had such sweet wine before.

900
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:06,880
Have you done?

901
00:40:08,530 --> 00:40:09,450
Can we drink now?

902
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:10,960
Drink what?

903
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,560
- I'll decide?
- You decide.

904
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,160
I can't drink that.

905
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,000
Come on.

906
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:21,960
Let's mix it.

907
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,200
Drink.

908
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,680
- Drink!
- Drink!

909
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:29,280
Whoever drinks slowly
drinks another one.

910
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:30,840
Good. Come on, let's drink.

911
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:32,280
We'll drink for everyone.

912
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:34,320
Take it easy. Don't pretend to be tough.

913
00:40:36,160 --> 00:40:37,000
Look at you.

914
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,920
You're a fountain!

915
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:40,400
What are you...

916
00:40:41,280 --> 00:40:42,120
What are you doing?

917
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:47,380
Someone accused Bao Chenyan
of hiring a killer.

918
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:48,560
After our investigation,

919
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:49,600
we suspect Bao Chenyan

920
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:51,040
may be involved in two murders.

921
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,320
Please cooperate with us.

922
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,440
Wait.

923
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,060
Did Xing Liang send you here?

924
00:40:55,080 --> 00:40:55,920
Shut up.

925
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,360
What's going on?

926
00:40:57,560 --> 00:40:58,440
Wait a second.

927
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:07,720
Xing Liang,

928
00:41:08,290 --> 00:41:10,080
how could Bao be involved
in a murder case?

929
00:41:10,740 --> 00:41:12,800
He almost died himself.
How could he kill someone?

930
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:15,020
Why don't you say
we're all murderers in this family?

931
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:16,880
Now, all the evidence points to him.

932
00:41:17,770 --> 00:41:19,600
Whether it's him or not,
we will investigate.

933
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,040
But he must be detained.

934
00:41:21,200 --> 00:41:22,160
That's it.

935
00:41:22,940 --> 00:41:24,180
(Xuan)
You...

936
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,720
What the hell?

937
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,240
Let's go.

938
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:49,620
(Inspection)

939
00:41:49,620 --> 00:41:53,460
(Binjiang Criminal Police Unit)

940
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:56,360
Zixuan.

941
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:01,320
I didn't kill anyone.

942
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:02,440
I'll be fine.

943
00:42:05,960 --> 00:42:06,810
Bao Chenyan,

944
00:42:06,820 --> 00:42:08,560
this is your arrest warrant.
Come with us.

945
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,240
Bao.

946
00:42:33,320 --> 00:42:34,160
Bao.

947
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:36,960
The battery's dead.

948
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:38,040
Keep it safe.

949
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,080
Got it.

950
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:42,640
Wait a minute.

951
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:02,680
Take him away.

952
00:43:38,591 --> 00:43:42,101
The moon is surrounded by stars

953
00:43:42,641 --> 00:43:46,531
I hide my regrets in the dark

954
00:43:47,291 --> 00:43:49,351
You said don't go

955
00:43:49,601 --> 00:43:54,891
Because that's where you belong

956
00:43:57,151 --> 00:44:00,711
Wild winds blow across the land

957
00:44:01,171 --> 00:44:05,221
Witnessing the hardships
we've been through

958
00:44:05,931 --> 00:44:08,251
You said don't be afraid

959
00:44:08,251 --> 00:44:12,801
Even though life is always hard

960
00:44:13,951 --> 00:44:15,871
Looking back

961
00:44:15,871 --> 00:44:18,531
My laughters and tears

962
00:44:18,531 --> 00:44:20,431
You've seen them all

963
00:44:20,431 --> 00:44:23,131
I've loved, got hurt, and made mistakes

964
00:44:23,131 --> 00:44:25,111
Maybe it's in the past

965
00:44:25,111 --> 00:44:26,671
Still remember

966
00:44:27,241 --> 00:44:32,471
The promises I made

967
00:44:32,971 --> 00:44:34,501
Dream about those years

968
00:44:34,501 --> 00:44:37,181
Waking up feeling painful

969
00:44:37,181 --> 00:44:39,171
On those lonely nights

970
00:44:39,171 --> 00:44:41,841
I couldn't sleep

971
00:44:41,841 --> 00:44:43,811
Praying for a good ending

972
00:44:43,811 --> 00:44:45,551
All that's left

973
00:44:45,551 --> 00:44:50,651
Is a sigh

974
00:44:57,741 --> 00:44:59,201
How I wish

975
00:44:59,821 --> 00:45:06,351
I could see you again
